data.description: You won't want to miss this affordably priced, one owner home located at the end of a quiet culdesac.  This wonderful 3 bedrooms and 2 bath rancher is ready for you to call home.  All appliances stay, including the washer and dryer.  Easy to care for laminate flooring in the living room, a large eat-in kitchen, pantry, large main level laundry, and two full baths.  You'll love the 7 x 8 master closet affording you plenty of room for your clothes in an already large master suite.  Plenty of space in the yard to park an RV.  Seller will purchase a Home Warranty.
